title: ISecondaryMemberUpToMembersFeatureData.GetFromPointMembers
description: Gets the structure system member(s) connected to a from point to create one or more secondary structure system up-to members.
remarks:
This method is valid only if
ISecondaryMemberUpToMembersFeatureData::MemberPointParametersType
is set to
swSecondaryMemberUpToMembersMemberPointParameters_e
.swSecondaryMemberUpToMembersMemberPointParameters_FromPoint.
